title: How to Style a Side Part | AXE | Instagroom
description:
Matteo is a perfectionist. His right side is always right.

THE TOOLS:
AXE Signature Clean Cut Look Classic Pomade 

THE STEPS:
1. Blow-dry 
2. Rub pomade through hair
3. Part with a comb
4. Swoop to the right

Subscribe to the AXE channel for more grooming tips.

transcripts: My good side is the right side, I use the blow dryer, I take a lot of pomade and I rub it through my hair. Then I take a comb, I part it on the left and I sweep it to the right. Yes, definitely my right side is the best one.
